{"tid":1726821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"解放軍可以隨意走出黎，咪更顯得政府垃圾囉","createTime":"2019-11-16T09:17:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T09:32:40.000Z","uid":229880,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"969e25a7ddc82b2bba8ece8895a4cc9b5f46829b","tid":1726821,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:17:47.000Z","msg":"對方以為咁樣可以拎民意去區選，<br />\n完全錯唒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家係解放軍自己走出黎，我地應該<strong>煲大政府搞5個月都搞唔掂，突顯政府同保皇黨完全無用</strong><br />\n<br />\n何況，香港呢幾個月以黎，封路只係其中一種手段，<br />\n我地一直係爭取緊五大訴求，開返條路，唔代表政府有回應市民要求<br />\n又唔代表星期一可以順利返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加上，好多巴打都提到基本法第十四條<br />\n中央人民政府派駐香港特別行政區負責防務的軍隊<strong>不干預</strong>香港特別行政區的地方事務。香港特別行政區政府在必要時，可向中央人民政府請求駐軍協助維持社會治安和救助災害。<br />\n<br />\n即係自發行動又違犯多條基本法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁個政府同基本法仲有咩野用呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ff76a1a0c74d0bfe5e74e2c5b6f73c4f2a2ed8","tid":1726821,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:17:54.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"9dda01c6c70ee6f7d4eb506a11ff9eb6abc4395d","tid":1726821,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:18:04.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"527347a9a79c4f6ff2b88f2954ce0138bfced58d","tid":1726821,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:18:26.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"2bbde5e120cb307947f967144c59d9b76176967f","tid":1726821,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:18:37.000Z","msg":"自推4/10"},{"pid":"44d0bb0e575070fc2302dfd2309dd8b312deb128","tid":1726821,"uid":24833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:18:37.000Z","msg":"正解"},{"pid":"547cd45cd4adc59245d1805e13338a3be474